*'''Referee:''' [[Terry McAulay]]
{{col-2}}
*'''Game attendance:''' 64,001 at [[Heinz Field]] in [[Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania]]
*'''TV announcers:''' ([[NFL on CBS|CBS]]) [[Gus Johnson (sportscaster)|Gus Johnson]] and [[Randy Cross]]
*'''Game coverage:''' [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/29536/PIT_Gamebook.pdf NFL Game Summary], [http://www.nfl.com/videos?videoId=09000d5d80a99841 NFL Films highlights]
