*Sunday, September 14 at 8:15 PM EDT ([[NBC Sunday Night Football]])
*'''Game weather:''' Cloudy, 80<U+00B0>F, Wind: SSW 40 mph
*'''Referee:''' [[Tony Corrente]]
{{col-2}}
*'''Game attendance:''' 73,048 at [[Cleveland Browns Stadium]] in [[Cleveland, Ohio]]
*'''TV announcers:''' ([[National Broadcasting Company|NBC]]) [[Al Michaels]], [[John Madden (American football)|John Madden]], and [[Andrea Kremer]]
*'''Game coverage:''' [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/29558/CLV_Gamebook.pdf NFL Game Summary], [http://www.nfl.com/videos?videoId=09000d5d80ad1733 NFL GameDay highlights]
{{col-end}}
