{{col-2}}
*'''Game attendance:''' 69,144 at [[Lincoln Financial Field]] in [[Philadelphia|Philadelphia, Pennsylvania]]
*'''TV announcers:''' (CBS) [[Jim Nantz]] and [[Phil Simms]]
*'''Game coverage:''' [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/29573/PHI_Gamebook.pdf NFL Game Summary], [http://www.nfl.com/videos?videoId=09000d5d80aff6d2 NFL Films highlights]
