*'''Game attendance:''' 64,991 at Heinz Field in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania
*'''TV announcers:''' ([[NFL on FOX|FOX]]) [[Dick Stockton]], [[Troy Aikman]], and [[Pam Oliver]]
*'''Game coverage:''' [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/29641/PIT_Gamebook.pdf NFL Game Summary], [http://www.nfl.com/videos?videoId=09000d5d80bf89bd NFL Network highlights]
