*'''Referee:''' [[Scott Green (American football official)|Scott Green]]
{{col-2}}
*'''Game attendance:''' 62,051 at Heinz Field in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania
*'''TV announcers:''' (CBS) Jim Nantz and Phil Simms
*'''Game coverage:''' [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/29685/PIT_Gamebook.pdf NFL Game Summary], [http://www.nfl.com/videos?videoId=09000d5d80c8a508 NFL Films highlights]
