*Sunday, December 14 at 4:15 PM EST
*'''Game weather:''' 45&nbsp;<U+00B0>F, Mostly Cloudy
*'''Referee:''' [[Walt Coleman]]
{{col-2}}
*'''Game attendance:''' 71,502 at [[M&T Bank Stadium]] in [[Baltimore|Baltimore, Maryland]]
*'''TV announcers:''' (CBS) Jim Nantz and Phil Simms
*'''Game coverage:''' [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/29738/BLT_Gamebook.pdf NFL Game Summary], [http://www.nfl.com/videos?videoId=09000d5d80d4fba4 NFL Films highlights]
{{col-end}}
