=== Wild Card round: Bye week ===
The team rested on December 29<U+2014>the day following their final regular season game. They began preparations for their first post-season game on Tuesday, December 30 through Thursday, January 1, before three days of weekend rest.<ref>{{cite news |first= Ed|last= Bouchette|title= Steelers Notebook: Pass-happy Hines Ward makes his 800th catch|url= http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/08364/938287-66.stm|work= Holiday pay|publisher= ''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette''|date= 29 December 2008|accessdate=29 December 2008}}</ref> Roethlisberger did not practice until Monday, January 5<ref name=Roex>{{cite news |title= Roethlisberger practices, expects to play|url= http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/playoffs2008/news/story?id=3811512|publisher= ESPN.com|date= 5 January 2009|accessdate=5 January 2009}}</ref><U+2014>Tomlin stated of the injury, "We will proceed slowly with him because we have that luxury. But we feel comfortable with where he is relative to Sunday and where he<U+2019>s capable of being next week."<ref>{{cite news |first= Alan|last= Robinson|title= Ben (Ben) headache? Steelers awaiting QB<U+2019>s return|url= http://sports.yahoo.com/nfl/news?slug=ap-idlesteelers&prov=ap&type=lgns|publisher= Yahoo! Sports|date= 30 December 2008|accessdate=2 January 2009}}</ref> Although the January 1 practice was expected to be normal, Tomlin allowed players to leave after team meetings and a walk-through.<ref>{{cite news |first= Gerry|last= Dulac|title= Steelers Notebook: Parker not expecting surgery|url= http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/09002/939112-66.stm?cmpid=sports.xml|work= New Year's break|publisher= ''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette''|date= 2 January 2009|accessdate=4 January 2009}}</ref> Multiple Steelers stated that they would watched the games of the Wild Card round. Some including James Farrior and Ryan Clark watched as fans, however, Chris Hoke said, "I will be watching the guys I am going against... That is how I watch it."<ref>{{cite news |first= Teresa|last= Varley|title= Steelers set to be spectators|url= http://news.steelers.com/article/101608/|publisher= PittsburghSteelers.com|date=2 January 2009|accessdate=4 January 2009}}</ref>

